| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0970 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6b49fc89-1fb2-5c81-9e59-ae7cdf4fb768"
